Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.42,0:01:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 因为是试做
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.82,0:01:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,先做200g试试看吧 白玉团子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.67,0:01:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.02,0:01:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,名字就叫凉白玉糖浆 可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.13,0:01:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 绝对很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.54,0:01:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,每年惯例的夏天的商店街祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.87,0:01:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,三日月堂也要出摊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.74,0:02:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,今年 爷爷把点心设计交给了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.37,0:02:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,白玉团子的做法 简单说来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.60,0:02:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,一 把白玉粉加水搅拌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.56,0:02:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,二 团起来煮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.98,0:02:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.84,0:02:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧 很简单吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.48,0:02:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,简单… 真的太简单了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.09,0:02:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,白玉粉200g 大约配160cc水
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.36,0:02:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,在碗里放粉 然后一点点加水搅拌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.34,0:02:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,拌匀后使劲揉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.31,0:02:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,加水太多会发粘难以团成团
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.89,0:02:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,加水到白玉粉成团就可以
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.46,0:02:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,用手揉成棒状
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.77,0:02:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,掐成一口大小
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.49,0:02:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我开始掌握要领了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.13,0:02:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,做这个好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.93,0:03:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,团子 这个是小桃的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.58,0:03:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,小桃做的真好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.00,0:03:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不过有点大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.40,0:03:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐 这么大行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.69,0:03:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,太小了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.83,0:03:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,小~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.42,0:03:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,圆的就行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.20,0:03:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系 煮过会膨胀一点 大小正好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.65,0:03:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,如果白玉团子比较大 就这样捏出个豁口来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.52,0:03:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,但这次是小粒的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.68,0:03:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,然后把它放进沸水里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.96,0:03:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,过上两三分钟就会咕嘟咕嘟浮起来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.92,0:03:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,还差一点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.17,0:03:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,再煮一会儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.73,0:03:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,然后再煮1分钟左右
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.54,0:03:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,放进冰水里 凉一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.46,0:03:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,好 完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.19,0:03:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.68,0:03:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs54}Q弹~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.06,0:03:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好快 好简单
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.20,0:03:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.06,0:03:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 先简单的用砂糖酱油
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.02,0:04:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.18,0:04:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,QQ的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.86,0:04:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,白玉团子自身这样就好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.39,0:04:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,问题在于糖浆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.68,0:04:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,有抹茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.70,0:04:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,梅子糖浆 凉小豆汤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.59,0:04:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,果然抹茶的好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.00,0:04:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,可是抹茶太贵了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.44,0:04:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不想卖一杯300日元以上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.86,0:04:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,白玉粉200g
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.48,0:04:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,大概可以做小个儿白玉丸子60个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.26,0:04:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,呃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.58,0:04:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,对了 那凉奶茶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.53,0:04:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,微微带点甜味
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.07,0:04:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,似乎不错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.69,0:04:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,确实红茶的茶叶要便宜得多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.76,0:04:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那不如连黑珍珠都放进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.18,0:04:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,也能点缀一下颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.76,0:05:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.27,0:05:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这个好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.90,0:05:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,既然黑珍珠要花钱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.66,0:05:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,容器和勺子不用一次性的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.86,0:05:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,而是把咱家和三日月堂的 还有美咲阿姨店里的聚集起来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,洗过循环利用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.21,0:05:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然有点累
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.66,0:05:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,对了 让桐山君来洗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.58,0:05:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好办法 就拜托他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.59,0:05:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,团子做的还不错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.76,0:05:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,有用冰水泡过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.09,0:05:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,然后是黑珍珠吗 真时髦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.48,0:05:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,口感真好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.00,0:05:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,这是淀粉的一种吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.42,0:05:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,外公
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.73,0:05:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,…这个怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.37,0:05:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.14,0:05:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶 真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.85,0:06:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉年轻人会喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.59,0:06:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,很适合在小摊上大卖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.06,0:06:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟是祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.06,0:06:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.46,0:06:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,特别是这个好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.61,0:06:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,梅子糖浆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.09,0:06:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,很爽口 好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.90,0:06:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这是千惠做的梅子糖浆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.79,0:06:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊 有股梅子香呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.88,0:06:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,放暑假之后不久
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.25,0:06:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我就去见千惠了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.72,0:06:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,千惠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.59,0:06:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,日向
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.74,0:06:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,她带我参观了牧场
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.68,0:06:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.32,0:06:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,陪我玩 汪汪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.26,0:06:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,陪我玩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.60,0:07:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,给我看了小花的小狗们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.60,0:07:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢 喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.19,0:07:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,交谈途中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.77,0:07:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,千惠有时会默默的发呆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.95,0:07:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,根据佐藤老师的说法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.26,0:07:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,千惠现在看到初中女生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.71,0:07:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,也会僵住动弹不了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.24,0:07:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,看到同龄的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.86,0:07:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,痛苦的事 难受的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.52,0:07:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,都会一股脑的涌向胸口和心头
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.88,0:07:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,身体在拼命的抵抗这一点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.12,0:08:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,为了一点点恢复像从前那样的说话行动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.56,0:08:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,千惠在这里一步一步的努力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.88,0:08:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,老师这样说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.46,0:08:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,傍晚 千惠发烧了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.59,0:08:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,她的妈妈开车把我们送去了车站
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.72,0:08:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,真的谢谢你和千惠做朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.36,0:08:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,她妈妈好多次握住了我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.45,0:08:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,她说会在这里和千惠一起加油
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.70,0:08:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,首先是交动物朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,然后是年长的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.93,0:08:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,第三个步骤是交同龄的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.97,0:09:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,千惠现在也在战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.88,0:09:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,给千惠发夏日祭的照片吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.50,0:09:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,大家在享用梅子糖浆的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.35,0:09:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,然后 还要再去见她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.62,0:09:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.85,0:09:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.89,0:09:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.65,0:09:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是三日月堂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.09,0:09:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,冰冰的 甜甜的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.88,0:09:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,冰镇白玉糖浆怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.66,0:09:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,冰冰甜甜的白玉糖浆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.49,0:09:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,冰镇的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.37,0:09:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,梅子糖浆久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.92,0:09:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.30,0:10:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,好好吃的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.24,0:10:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,新碗来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.85,0:10:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这边的收了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.47,0:10:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢 桐山君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.22,0:10:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,还有百日元硬币
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.69,0:10:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,拆两条放里面了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.27,0:10:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,还有抹布 新的挂这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.30,0:10:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,桐山君太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.77,0:10:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么这么了解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.01,0:10:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了 帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.72,0:10:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思 小子 让你帮这么大忙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.76,0:10:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,来喝冰镇糖浆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.39,0:10:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.60,0:10:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,客人好多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.80,0:10:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.05,0:10:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,盛况空前啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.90,0:10:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,连我这边都卖的很好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.34,0:10:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我第一次参加这种活动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.72,0:10:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉好吃惊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.00,0:10:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.48,0:10:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,桐山君 桐山君 来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.77,0:10:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.13,0:10:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.18,0:10:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 高桥君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.03,0:10:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 你是不是又变大了很多？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.52,0:11:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这是千惠做的梅子糖浆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.24,0:11:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.57,0:11:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好大个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.02,0:11:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,奶奶 美香子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.03,0:11:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃的三色团子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.94,0:11:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,要来一串吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.39,0:11:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.97,0:11:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.13,0:11:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,她们做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.38,0:11:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,真是个好晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.47,0:11:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,小零
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.38,0:11:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢这种的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.17,0:12:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,最喜欢这种了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.51,0:12:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.43,0:12:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.52,0:12:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,还不到7点 一转眼就卖了这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.35,0:12:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,现在的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.92,0:12:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,厨房里留着当晚饭的咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.84,0:12:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,也能卖到飞起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.82,0:12:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐 冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.75,0:12:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,咖喱不行 我们家是和果子店啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.86,0:12:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不好了 姐姐 白玉已经只剩一盒了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.18,0:12:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,明明做了这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.95,0:12:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,来煮吧 现在马上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.99,0:12:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了 因为糖浆已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.02,0:12:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会这样 难得是个大赚一笔的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.45,0:12:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.72,0:12:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不是还有黄豆粉和黑蜜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.29,0:12:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,外公
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.91,0:12:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,明里 烧水去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.56,0:12:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.38,0:12:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,日向这边拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.70,0:12:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.19,0:12:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,小子去买冰来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.37,0:13:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,问高桥家儿子就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.43,0:13:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.42,0:13:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我来做团子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.71,0:13:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好 川本家 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.46,0:13:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.97,0:13:11.98,SCREEN,,0,0,0,,{\an3\c&H7A6F72&\fs65\blur1\b1\pos(1785,1060)}在 这 里
Comment: 0,0:12:19.96,0:12:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,==============================================B-Title==================================================
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.98,0:13:15.98,SCREEN,,0,0,0,,{\an1\c&HC0F35D&\fs65\blur1\b1\pos(132,450)}暑 假{\fs42}  ①
Comment: 0,0:22:54.69,0:22:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,==============================================B-PART=================================================
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.35,0:13:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.19,0:13:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,三月町祭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.47,0:13:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,多准备点糖浆就好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.85,0:13:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,没想到7点就卖光了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.68,0:13:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,好浪费
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.62,0:13:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,话说你们成本太高了  送太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.95,0:13:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,费那么大劲才赚这么点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.04,0:13:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,可真是赔本赚吆喝了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.64,0:13:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.41,0:13:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,客人来了这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.22,0:13:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,果然会让人热血沸腾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.34,0:13:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,多亏来了好多客人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.56,0:14:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,平时的点心也卖出好多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.61,0:14:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,吸引顾客的拳头商品果然重要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.34,0:14:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,超市说牛奶一盒128日元也会去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.84,0:14:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,鸡胸肉100g68日元
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.18,0:14:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,西红柿罐一个78日元什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.61,0:14:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,其他的东西当然也会一并买了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.19,0:14:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你们的妈妈和外婆也很会卖东西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.34,0:14:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,甜的 咸的 不管做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.32,0:14:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,总能让顾客排长队
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.26,0:14:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,每次祭典 我都觉得真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.46,0:14:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,真想让你们也看看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.47,0:14:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我还记得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.94,0:14:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,喵喵烧 花花烧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.22,0:14:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,大大的蝴蝶结的袋子 好可爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.07,0:14:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,她们常说不要花钱 要用心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.23,0:15:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我也帮忙包装了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.01,0:15:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.17,0:15:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你们作为第一次已经做的很好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.58,0:15:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然销售额 手法和预判都还差点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.92,0:15:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,明年也可以继续交给你们哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.91,0:15:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,真的？ 可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.82,0:15:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我会加油的 像妈妈和外婆那样让顾客排起长队来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.64,0:15:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,得快点去考虑菜单才行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.28,0:15:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,日向 冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.22,0:15:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,或者说先要考试
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.67,0:15:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,要报哪个学校？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.25,0:15:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,对了 想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.81,0:15:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,明天是暑期考试
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.19,0:15:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然是暑假 但也要去上学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.34,0:15:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,出题范围已经学过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.79,0:15:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 学了 虽然还剩了一点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.83,0:15:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,对了 姐姐 果冻怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.35,0:15:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,手停下了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.56,0:15:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,快点包
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.05,0:15:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,铜锣烧都要干了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.75,0:15:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.32,0:15:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,外公 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.90,0:16:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 我… 做不来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.56,0:16:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对不行 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.70,0:16:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,3A的班主任 不行 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.06,0:16:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,没事没事 多半…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.59,0:16:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,姑且还有我在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.48,0:16:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,担子太重了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.68,0:16:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你看到了吧 那个高城家长的态度
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.27,0:16:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我绝对没自信和她周旋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.63,0:16:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,换班主任了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.93,0:16:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,要把重要的初三后期交给这么年轻的家伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.70,0:16:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,学校在想什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.98,0:16:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 我还是新人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.31,0:16:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你要是新人我就是老人！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.27,0:16:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不如说要我负责两个班 体力上完全不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.55,0:16:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,一个人怎么可能看得过来90人！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.42,0:16:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我还有年级主任的工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.78,0:17:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,而且 和高城的谈话 要持续到什么时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.44,0:17:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我说过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.34,0:17:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,让她知道自己做了什么 也是工作的一环
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.15,0:17:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然你这样说…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.80,0:17:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不论对她再说什么都没用了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.78,0:17:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,因为她自己决定不要去理解罪恶感这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.84,0:17:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么要对她费这么大力气
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.14,0:17:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,多奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.74,0:17:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,给人添麻烦的一方反而受到这么多照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.90,0:17:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,被欺负的佐仓千惠不仅转学了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.32,0:17:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,在对面也还没能上学呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.07,0:17:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,让一百步 就算她真的没有恶意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.47,0:17:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不如说 都做到这个地步了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.18,0:17:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不论有没有恶意都是一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.06,0:17:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,小见川…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.56,0:17:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我要写在档案里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.28,0:18:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,作为新班主任
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.81,0:18:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,把真正情况一五一十写出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.80,0:18:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,独善其身 对其他人攻击性强
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.14,0:18:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,作为集团首领
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.37,0:18:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,在班级内部引起了大规模问题
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.46,0:18:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,对于自己造成的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.64,0:18:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,谁都必须负起责任
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.33,0:18:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我这样想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.36,0:18:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,必须受到报应
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.43,0:18:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不然很奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.52,0:18:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我说 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.15,0:18:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,有答案了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.58,0:18:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,所有人都必须努力的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.12,0:19:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你找了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.26,0:19:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 那之后我想了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.43,0:19:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.13,0:19:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,没能找到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.54,0:19:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,没能找到是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.02,0:19:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,那算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.64,0:19:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我绞尽了脑汁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.42,0:19:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,但仔细想想 一个都没能想出来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.34,0:19:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,真是不可思议啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.99,0:19:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,这么说来 仔细想想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.52,0:19:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我对于这一点从来没有怀疑过
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.64,0:19:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.67,0:19:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然努力很累
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.52,0:19:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,但我只知道必须去做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.96,0:19:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不知不觉间
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.32,0:20:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,都会到达“努力是为了自己”
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.48,0:20:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,已经不记得是谁说的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.81,0:20:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,还是从哪里读到的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.27,0:20:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这么司空见惯的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.02,0:20:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,到了这一把年纪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.73,0:20:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,终于发自内心的想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.38,0:20:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 这句话是真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.07,0:20:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我长久以来肯定只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.74,0:20:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,想要做个比现在更好的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.73,0:20:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,突然说起自己的事了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.73,0:20:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,会很长吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.71,0:20:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不会的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.79,0:20:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,到时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.04,0:20:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你们班的临时班主任就做到今天为止
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.28,0:20:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,高城
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.08,0:20:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在多半不安到无可奈何吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.26,0:21:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,什么都没有做过 连自己的极限都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.78,0:21:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不安的原因就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.01,0:21:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,老师？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.74,0:21:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你之所以提不起干劲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.03,0:21:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是因为害怕知道自己的极限而失望
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.01,0:21:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,可是高城
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.88,0:21:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,失望也不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.95,0:21:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,只有知道自己的极限在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.31,0:21:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,才能知道应当去做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.80,0:21:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,只要搞清楚自己的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.69,0:21:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,就能渐渐看到自己想做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.30,0:21:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这样一来 就能从现在这份极度不安中解放出来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.88,0:21:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,只有这一点 我可以保证
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.17,0:21:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,考试结束后的晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.63,0:22:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我画了好多画
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.97,0:22:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,脑子里冒出好多颜色漂亮的点心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.28,0:22:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不断冒出来 冒出来 停不下来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.90,0:22:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,日向 还要熬夜到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.02,0:22:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,快点去泡澡…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.93,0:22:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,还开着风扇 会感冒的 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.58,0:22:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,日向…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.04,0:22:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这么晚了搞什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.13,0:22:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.39,0:22:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.38,0:22:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,全都看起来好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.47,0:22:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.39,0:22:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,好兴奋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.27,0:23:00.02,SCREEN,,0,0,0,,{\an3\c&H7A6F72&\fs65\blur1\b1\pos(1795,1060)}暑 假{\fs42}  ①
Comment: 0,0:23:00.02,0:23:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,==============================================C-PART================================================
